Class GamesHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.server.GamesHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnswerEventHandler, AnswerEventReceiver
    public class GamesHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements AnswerEventHandler, AnswerEventReceiver
    This class waits for user input and sends it to the right controller It associate every nickname to a specific Receiver and Controller Every Receiver has 1 nickname Every Controller has multiple nicknames
